# Production build (used for `vite build`, e.g. Railway single-service deploy
# where this same Express process also serves the built frontend). Empty =
# API calls go to the same origin the page was loaded from, no separate
# backend URL needed. Vite's mode-specific .env.production overrides .env for
# builds - see https://vite.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html#env-files.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
